Package engine

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Centrality
    This class provides implementations of the various centrality measures of the Graph Toolkit, including betweeness cetnrality and PageRank.
    DataReader
    This class provides methods for reading the data from various sources into the Graph class.
    Edge
    This class provides an Edge object, with associated methods.
    Flow
    This class provides implementations of the various algorithms dealing with flow in the Graph Toolkit, including Edmonds-Karp.
    Graph
    This class provides an implementation of a Graph object, with a Set of Nodes and associated methods.
    GraphToolkit
    This class provides access to all of the algorithms found in the Centrality, Flow, and Search classes.
    Node
    This class provides an implementation of a generic Node object with associated methods.
    Recommender
    This class provides various scoring methods, along with a collaborative filtering recommendation algorithm.
    Search
    This class provides implementations of the various search algorithms from the Graph Toolkit class, including BFS, DFS, Topological Sort, and Floyd-Warshall.
